column5: http://s1204.photobucket.com/user/tennis_pwn/media/P1010323.jpg.html?sort=3&o=0  It was not my targeted species, but a nice fish all the same.  Caught this trolling a yellow and blue Risto Rap.  It was quite rough out there; I was just going to head for some more sheltered water and try for some pike when this one hit.
was anxious to look at the 9 lb (record) smalley  ?????
Nice brownie...you got lucky to find one in there so early.
Jesus thought you landed a 9lb smallie. Nice brown!
Nice brown for sure !!!! And the funny thing is the risto rap is their fav lure !!!!! We used them for years and caught tons !!!!! Cheers
